      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideally suited for someone seeking a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently runs very roughly with a persistent knock, and the transmission is experiencing significant slipping. Externally, the body shows its age with several noticeable dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior has heavy tearing and stains. Please note that this car will likely require towing and extensive repairs to be driven safely again.",
